# Copy to `.env.local` for local dev. For GitHub Actions / Pages / Vercel, set the same keys in the host UI.
# `.env.local` is gitignored — do not commit real secrets you care about in git history.

# Project ref: lnwitmfmhmftvsiattmf
# Both are required for analytics + CONSOLE live stats.
